{"title":"大漠魂","authors":["洪三泰"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":4,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大漠魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪三泰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大漠乳黄的纸页里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坦克是用钢铁镶嵌的宣言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铮铮然从幽谷传出，尖厉、刻薄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一语点破古长城的封闭线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当代军人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站立在苍茫的天地之间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝重深沉的呐喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半给辐射的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半给放射的狼烟……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"米黄的天幕之下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群飞动的亮点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片凝炼闪光的语言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当代军人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站立在苍茫的天地之间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城以外还是长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群山之上更有群山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是边塞的又一奇迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁镶入古朴雄浑的字典。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}